As senators continue their
fight over health care, there
are new feuds bubbling on the

34:45.000 --> 34:47.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
other end of
Pennsylvania Avenue.

34:47.600 --> 34:51.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
From cracking down on
leaks to weighing Attorney
General Jeff Sessions'
future, and the president

