45:00.133 --> 45:04.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: We
close tonight with two
affectionate looks at Africa.

45:06.466 --> 45:11.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
First, a journalist's
love of the continent,
family and his craft.

45:13.466 --> 45:15.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Jeffrey Brown begins with
our latest addition to
the "NewsHour" Bookshelf.

45:15.966 --> 45:18.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: As a
19-year-old college
student, Jeffrey Gettleman
traveled to East Africa

45:18.866 --> 45:20.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
and fell in love with a place.

45:20.766 --> 45:23.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
