of Africa, we turn to
another in our Brief
But Spectacular series,

51:31.366 --> 51:33.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
where we ask people to
describe their passions.

51:33.466 --> 51:37.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Tonight, Kenyan filmmaker Wanuri
Kahiu, who's using a new style
to tell modern African stories.

51:39.966 --> 51:43.666 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WANURI KAHIU, Filmmaker: I am
a filmmaker and storyteller.

51:43.666 --> 51:48.666 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And I have made films
and written stories
about rusted robots that
fall in love, Nairobi

51:50.700 --> 51:55.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
pop bands that want to go to
space, girls who want to race
camels in the future, girls

51:57.033 --> 52:00.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
who want to dance in the
future, anything that's fun,
fizz, and frivolous coming out

52:00.266 --> 52:04.200 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of Africa.

52:04.200 --> 52:09.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
A couple of years ago, I was
writing a love story, and I
was looking for funding for it.

52:12.833 --> 52:17.833 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And when I said I was
looking for a love
story, and I approached
investors, one of them to

52:19.733 --> 52:23.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
me, if you add a rape
scene, then we might be able
to get you some funding.

52:23.900 --> 52:25.366 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And this was devastating to me.

52:25.366 --> 52:30.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It felt as if Africans just
can't fall in love or be joyous.

52:30.200 --> 52:33.433 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
There has to be some sort of
tragedy linked to their love.

52:33.433 --> 52:36.400 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And I completely,
completely reject that idea.

52:36.400 --> 52:41.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so I pushed back with this
idea of Afro Bubble Gum art
that means we can be just for

52:43.033 --> 52:44.266 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
being's sake.

52:44.266 --> 52:46.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We can just create
for creating's sake.

52:46.166 --> 52:49.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
It doesn't have
to have an issue.

52:49.000 --> 52:51.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I always knew I wanted
to create stories.

52:51.066 --> 52:56.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But the more I started to
create, I started to realize
that I wasn't seeing myself in

52:56.666 --> 52:58.766 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
these films.

52:58.766 --> 53:02.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
All I could do was write stories
that represented the people
that I knew and the people that

53:02.133 --> 53:04.166 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I grew up with.

